Detailed Description

Frame Skip parameters. Not all interface support this, please refer interface specific header.

Field Documentation

UInt32 Vps_CaptFrameSkip::chNum

[IN] Channel number of which frame skip will be applied.

UInt32 Vps_CaptFrameSkip::frmSkipMask

[IN] Frame Skip Mask (bit0..bit29) bitN = 1 Skip frame, bitN = 0 DO NOT skip frame Example, 0x0 for no frame skip, 0x2AAAAAAA for skipping alternate frames.
